  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Telegram机器人的完整处理流程。用户发消息到@bot，然后我们要判断是不是需要处理的指令，比如@bot或者!eval前缀的消息。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Telegram",
        "mention/@bot",
        "prefix: !eval"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，入口是Telegram。那消息先到哪儿？直接进业务逻辑还是先有个接收层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Telegram",
        "Webhook Server"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "先过Webhook Server，跑在8080端口。Telegram用POST推Update过来，然后Webhook Server调用HandleUpdate把update对象传给业务层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Telegram",
        "Webhook Server (:8080)",
        "POST /webhook (Update)",
        "HandleUpdate(update)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以Telegram→Webhook Server是POST /webhook，Web→App是HandleUpdate。业务层我们叫UseCase: EvaluateMsg对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Webhook Server (:8080)",
        "UseCase: EvaluateMsg",
        "HandleUpdate(update)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对。EvaluateMsg里面先做Gate判断，过滤掉不是@bot也不是!eval的消息。然后过RateLimit和Moderation检查，防刷和风控。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UseCase: EvaluateMsg",
        "Gate (mention/@bot or prefix: !eval)",
        "RateLimit & Moderation check"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Gate和RateLimit都是App自己内部处理，不用调外部服务？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UseCase: EvaluateMsg",
        "Gate (mention/@bot or prefix: !eval)",
        "RateLimit & Moderation check"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，这两个都是自包含的校验逻辑。过了之后要分三种引擎模式处理：纯LLM、纯MCP、还有Hybrid混合模式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Engine = LLM",
        "Engine = MCP",
        "Engine = Hybrid"
