      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我画一个alt分支。第一种情况Engine=LLM，App调用LLM Client做Analyze，传入message，返回summary/eval。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UseCase: EvaluateMsg",
